{"tid":1416571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家冷靜","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:36:06.000Z","uid":3896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6114d51ab8ebab3e07ba4d672c43e89a27a71e90","tid":1416571,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我知大家好嬲<br />\n我都好嬲<br />\n但唔可以比憤怒支配<br />\n我地唔係要泄憤<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔想再有手足流血比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以回一回氣先<br />\n比和理非做住主軸先<br />\n<br />\n香港始終係和理非大多數<br />\n如果一直衝突會比到機會對家逆轉民意<br />\n可唔可以冷靜落嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都好攰 好攰....<br />\n做好文宣, 暫停勇武 唔可以熱情冷卻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我想有一日<br />\n大家可以除裝備<br />\n望吓身邊嘅手足係咩樣<br />\n然後比大家一個擁抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"83d5aeb5ce37cfc8da9f48e794a4e6bc70b30d5f","tid":1416571,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e7b14bdbbeff15d4cd5452c1f8ff6d084b8ac6","tid":1416571,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"和理非請你永遠記住<br />\n&quot;不割蓆&quot;唔係叫你要認同哂所有抗爭手段，你絕對可以隨時提出意見；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;不割蓆&quot; 意思係叫你就算點都好，都唔好離隊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;絕不放棄，抗爭到底，直到勝利&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n[ 溫故知新！] 成日話&quot;不割蓆&quot;, 都想大家深入明白咩叫&quot;不割蓆&quot;先！！(利申：不割)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a767a20bdc0b3da5277549733aac694f4d5f78d2","tid":1416571,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望大家可以冷靜諗一諗"},{"pid":"46bd9ab70fd47f741f150a09a3d5bb8bc78a8f5c","tid":1416571,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"香港示威者已經好冷靜克制 唔好自己嚇自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"38e6b7efe3eec32a8b223b3dd7a482a630f3e661","tid":1416571,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"992d65e1616192f66f573338d7bc1dae36ae5460","tid":1416571,"uid":3896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"轉主調 唔等於割蓆<br />\n唔係放棄 停手<br />\n<br />\n太密勇武 大家會攰, 會少咗一d人出嚟<br />\n會更加危險, 大家回一回氣先好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775ea31304d6cf6713599e76555513e35e43e3b3","tid":1416571,"uid":152440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:23:41.000Z","msg":"要比市民知道我地同popo 係唔一樣。<br />\n我哋係有思考既示威者，唔係POPO亂咬人。"},{"pid":"2319308d8bc06894f8a4163ed635f736f50ed7e1","tid":1416571,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"最後一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}